/i
#char 15
/i/i
#loop
:touch
#play tcf+c
The lamp is still warm. You must have
only just fallen asleep. The bulb hums
its small amber hum, throwing everything
into sharp, kind focus.
Nothing here has begun to soften yet.
#end
    end

    stat at 44,17 element Object cycle 2 p1 cp437:0x0E under Empty color 0x00
    oop
@you-waking
#end
:touch
#play tefgc
You are awake inside the dream, and it
knows it. Colors sit exactly where they
belong. You can read the spines of the
books. You can count the folds in the
quilt.
$Somewhere, a door you love is open.
It is to the east. It always was.
#end
    end
  end
end

