  stats
    stat at 29,13 element Passage cycle 0 p3 board "The Long Hallway" under Empty color 0x00

    stat at 24,13 element Object cycle 2 p1 cp437:0x0E under Empty color 0x00
    oop
@receiver
#end
:touch
#play tcega
The receiver is warm. You lift it and
listen. Cloud drifts through the glass.
/i
A voice, unmistakable, a little far away:
$--- so glad you called. Where are you?
/i
You open your mouth. The clouds thicken
around the booth, muffling the line.
/i
:again
#zap touch
#play tfdca
You press the receiver harder to your ear.
$--- promise you'll remember the ---
/i
Static swallows the rest. The voice thins,
folding into the hiss like a name you can
almost say and then cannot.
/i
:last
#zap again
#play tc-a-f-c
Only your own breathing on the line now.
The cord runs up into the fog and stops.
/i
You set the receiver down, gently, the way
you would close a door on someone sleeping.
#end
    end
  end
end

