    stat at 6,19 element Object cycle 3 p1 cp437:0x01 under Normal color 0x08
    oop
@f7
#end
:touch
#play tc
Half a face. The other half has already
gone wherever the forgotten things go.
#end

    end
    stat at 14,19 element Object cycle 3 p1 cp437:0x02 under Normal color 0x08
    oop
@f8
#end
