@lamp
#end
:touch
#play tc-e
The lamp on the table is cold.
No one has lit it in a long time.
You reach for the switch and cannot
remember whose hand used to be here.
#zap touch
#end
:touch
#play td-f
Just a cold lamp. Just an empty table.
#end

    end
    stat at 20,16 element Object cycle 3 p1 cp437:0xF9 under Empty color 0x08
    oop
@nameplate
#end
:touch
#play te-g
A small nameplate rests here, face up.
The engraving has worn smooth.
You know a name belongs here.
You wait for it to come. It does not.
#zap touch
#end
:touch
#play tf-a
The nameplate is blank. You let it be.
#end

    end
    stat at 45,17 element Object cycle 1 p1 cp437:0x04 under Empty color 0x08
    oop
@acceptance
#end
:touch
#play tcega
So this is the empty room.
The lamp is cold. The name is gone.
And still the quiet does not hurt
the way you were so afraid it would.
#play ie
You loved someone. That part stays,
even when the shape of them does not.
#play tfa+c
You breathe out. You let the room
be empty. You let yourself wake.
#play gec.
#endgame

    end
  end
